<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Charts">Charts</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Nightmare_(Avenged_Sevenfold_song)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Charts"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>"Nightmare" debuted and peaked at number 51 on the <a href="/wiki/Billboard_Hot_100" title="Billboard Hot 100"><i>Billboard</i> Hot 100</a>. However, on the week ending August 14, 2010, the song re-entered at number 83 due to the release of the album.<sup id="cite_ref-14" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-14"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>14<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup> It is the band's highest-charting song in the United States and Canada.
</p>
